{
  "uid": "dma-rt-jitter",
  "title": "DMA RT / Jitter (S4)",
  "tags": [
    "dma",
    "rt",
    "jitter",
    "s4"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "editable": true,
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 2,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**DMA RT / Jitter (Track A S4)** \u2014 the EtherCAT master's per-cycle timing from `dma_main`'s `/metric_events` ring (`dma_debug_dma_*`). Cycle budget = **2000\u00b5s** (deadline), nominal baseline ~1850\u00b5s. Missed-deadline/WKC shown as **rate** (cumulative-since-boot totals are not jitter). Command path *spans*: see the `teleop_command_trace` dashboard / Tempo."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "RT cycle time (\u00b5s)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 2
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "\u00b5s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "dma_debug_dma_cycle_time_us",
          "legendFormat": "cycle mean"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "dma_debug_dma_cycle_time_us_max",
          "legendFormat": "cycle max"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
